As the halfway point of the season approaches, Giambi turns things around, with a little help from his upper lip. The Yankees first baseman grew a spectacular mustache, paying homage to his childhood hero Don Mattingly. The mustache became a craze in the Bronx, and earned Giambi the support of the American Mustache Institute (which actually exists) and led to a promotional giveaway at Yankee Stadium. "Jason Giambi Mustache Day" was a big hit, with thousands of people sporting mustaches ...
